setDetails.setDescription: The Meme Index(CMI) is a digital asset or token designed to track the performance of five tokens; four top meme tokens and a stablecoin. The meme index pool carries equal weight of the following tokens: C4G3, DOGE, SHIB, DOGELON, USDC.
setDetails.managerDescription: Cage Master is an African Blockchain enthusiasts and investor. He has been in the space since 2018 and have worked with a few Projects especially in the field of research and marketing. Founder of scrate.io and a core member of phoenix.io
